      <div class="gk-tip">
        <strong>Key entries to remember:</strong> Defence, Foreign affairs, Atomic energy → Union List. Public order, Police, Land → State List. Education (moved from State to Concurrent by 42nd Amendment, 1976), Forests, Weights &amp; Measures, Criminal law → Concurrent List. Residuary powers (subjects not in any list) → Parliament (Art. 248).
      </div>
    </div>

